text: Demetris Syllouris (; ; born 27 July 1953) is a Greek-Cypriot politician. He is the President of the Cypriot parliament since 2018. He was the leader of the European Party between 2005 and 2016. ==Other websites== * Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of the House of Representatives (Cyprus)
